      "content": "hey, my left eye is looking really red and it's kinda painful too. there's a lot of weird yellow gunk/discharge when i wake up. probably just dry eyes from being on my laptop all day at work, right? can i just use some regular lubricating eye drops from the drugstore to fix it?",
