      "content": "is it really okay though? i read somewhere that if it's a certain type of infection, putting stuff in your eye can actually cause permanent damage or scarring if you use the wrong thing. wouldn't it be way safer to just wait a day or two and see if the drops help before i try anything as strong as antibiotic ointment?",
